OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening and night with outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain spreading from the west. Rain
OL,8,Fpatchy across the Central Belt and the
OL,9,Feast. Strong southwesterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FRain, occasionally heavy,
OL,12,Fwill spread southeast across all parts
OL,13,Fin the morning. Then drier with a few
OL,14,Fshowers following on in the afternoon.
OL,15,FWindy at first.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCold on
OL,18,FFriday and Saturday with scattered
OL,19,Fwintry showers, these mainly across
OL,20,Fthe west. Rain spreading east followed
OL,21,Fby showers on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
